00:33:47.659 --> 00:33:49.361 align:middle line:84%
because they were using
these pharmaceutical

00:33:49.361 --> 00:33:52.797 align:middle line:90%
synthetic-derived hormones.

00:33:52.797 --> 00:33:56.568 align:middle line:84%
