than the general population

00:34:12.150 --> 00:34:14.985 align:middle line:84%
who did not use the
progesterone or estriol.

00:34:14.985 --> 00:34:18.255 align:middle line:84%
Not only did it not
equalize, but it was far less.

00:34:18.255 --> 00:34:20.659 align:middle line:84%
So there's protective
factors of these hormones

00:34:20.659 --> 00:34:23.628 align:middle line:84%
when used properly in the right
dosages and monitored correctly.

