00:36:29.254 --> 00:36:31.523 align:middle line:84%
or as you say plastic
bottled water and so forth.

00:36:31.523 --> 00:36:32.290 align:middle line:90%
>> Delgado: Right.

00:36:32.290 --> 00:36:33.491 align:middle line:90%
So let's -- let's be --

00:36:33.491 --> 00:36:35.260 align:middle line:84%
let's re-review the
possibility of that.

00:36:35.260 --> 00:36:37.429 align:middle line:90%
Let's say the person's smart;

00:36:37.429 --> 00:36:40.498 align:middle line:84%
they're not doing synthetic
birth control pills;

00:36:40.498 --> 00:36:41.533 align:middle line:90%
they're using natural methods

00:36:41.533 --> 00:36:43.635 align:middle line:84%
of birth control,
alternative methods.

00:36:43.635 --> 00:36:46.738 align:middle line:84%
They're not using
synthetic HRT...

00:36:46.738 --> 00:36:48.139 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:36:48.139 --> 00:36:49.674 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: ...estrogens
nor synthetic progesterones.

00:36:49.674 --> 00:36:51.176 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Okay.

00:36:51.176 --> 00:36:52.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: But they are still
using bioidentical estrogens

00:36:52.310 --> 00:36:55.013 align:middle line:90%
and bioidentical progesterone.

00:36:55.013 --> 00:36:56.281 align:middle line:84%
The problem is even the
bioidentical progesterone can

00:36:56.281 --> 00:37:00.185 align:middle line:84%
turn into one of the harmful
forms of estrogen downstream.

00:37:00.185 --> 00:37:03.354 align:middle line:84%
The biochemistry turns
eventually downstream to one

00:37:03.354 --> 00:37:05.490 align:middle line:84%
of these 40 estrogen
metabolites.

00:37:05.490 --> 00:37:06.991 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:37:06.991 --> 00:37:07.625 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: And most doctors
will never tell you this,

00:37:07.625 --> 00:37:09.194 align:middle line:90%
nor are they aware of it.

00:37:09.194 --> 00:37:11.096 align:middle line:84%
But I wrote the definitive
papers in winter of 2003,

00:37:11.096 --> 00:37:14.132 align:middle line:84%
and I did all the
research on cancer,

00:37:14.132 --> 00:37:15.366 align:middle line:84%
and the bioidentical
hormones, and the herbs.

00:37:15.366 --> 00:37:19.370 align:middle line:84%
So I believe that hormones
can be modified properly,

00:37:19.370 --> 00:37:20.638 align:middle line:90%
maybe like in ancient times.

00:37:20.638 --> 00:37:23.374 align:middle line:84%
We were designed to eat a
lot of raw, fresh, whole,

00:37:23.374 --> 00:37:26.678 align:middle line:84%
herbal plant-based foods,
and these herbs have a way

00:37:26.678 --> 00:37:30.515 align:middle line:84%
of modifying and protecting us
while we restore our hormones.

00:37:30.515 --> 00:37:32.684 align:middle line:84%
Ancient Chinese medicine
they were, as I mentioned,

00:37:32.684 --> 00:37:34.285 align:middle line:84%
drying the urine to
get the hormones.

00:37:34.285 --> 00:37:36.020 align:middle line:84%
But they weren't just
depending on that.

00:37:36.020 --> 00:37:38.389 align:middle line:84%
They were using herbal
and Chinese medicine

00:37:38.389 --> 00:37:41.092 align:middle line:84%
that goes back 3,000
years, and those herbs work.

00:37:41.092 --> 00:37:42.260 align:middle line:84%
I looked at Indian
herbs, Chinese herbs.

00:37:42.260 --> 00:37:44.429 align:middle line:90%
I studied the world.

00:37:44.429 --> 00:37:46.998 align:middle line:84%
I traveled all over the world,
and I met with the scientists.

00:37:46.998 --> 00:37:48.666 align:middle line:84%
And it's interesting. I'd go,
"You're Dr. So-and-so."

00:37:48.666 --> 00:37:51.269 align:middle line:84%
And you know they're researching
stem cells, and they'd look

00:37:51.269 --> 00:37:53.271 align:middle line:84%
at my name tag, "You're
Dr. Nick Delgado.

00:37:53.271 --> 00:37:54.506 align:middle line:90%
Wow!"

00:37:54.506 --> 00:37:56.241 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I was like I didn't
even know they knew me.

00:37:56.241 --> 00:37:57.575 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:37:57.575 --> 00:37:58.443 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: So other countries
know me better than they do

00:37:58.443 --> 00:37:59.110 align:middle line:90%
in my own country.

00:37:59.110 --> 00:38:00.345 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:38:00.345 --> 00:38:02.213 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: So all that being
said, it's exciting to know

00:38:02.213 --> 00:38:05.717 align:middle line:84%
that the natural wasabi
is 40 times higher

00:38:05.717 --> 00:38:07.485 align:middle line:90%
in isocyathyanase than broccoli.

00:38:07.485 --> 00:38:09.120 align:middle line:84%
So it has a protective
factor in the presence

00:38:09.120 --> 00:38:12.190 align:middle line:84%
of shifting the bad estrogens,
even from progesterone

00:38:12.190 --> 00:38:15.126 align:middle line:84%
and bioidentical, to
the good estrogens,

00:38:15.126 --> 00:38:17.495 align:middle line:84%
and then delivering
them out the body.

00:38:17.495 --> 00:38:19.998 align:middle line:84%
Wasabi, D-gluconolactone
which is similar

00:38:19.998 --> 00:38:21.199 align:middle line:90%
to calcium D-glucarate.

00:38:21.199 --> 00:38:22.634 align:middle line:90%
That's the patented version.

00:38:22.634 --> 00:38:24.169 align:middle line:90%
We use DYM, dymalmethane,

00:38:24.169 --> 00:38:25.236 align:middle line:84%
but I has to have a
delivery system along

00:38:25.236 --> 00:38:27.238 align:middle line:90%
with indole 3 carbinol.

00:38:27.238 --> 00:38:28.406 align:middle line:90%
And we use the correct dose,

00:38:28.406 --> 00:38:30.241 align:middle line:84%
because some people have
used indole 3 carbinol

00:38:30.241 --> 00:38:32.610 align:middle line:84%
at too high a dose, caused
some neurological issues,

00:38:32.610 --> 00:38:34.012 align:middle line:90%
so I always look at dosages.

00:38:34.012 --> 00:38:35.146 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: So what does
this look like on your site?

00:38:35.146 --> 00:38:36.481 align:middle line:84%
What would the product
look like?

00:38:36.481 --> 00:38:39.050 align:middle line:84%
Because you're using a lot
of terms that most people...

00:38:39.050 --> 00:38:40.285 align:middle line:90%
>> Delgado: I'm sorry.

00:38:40.285 --> 00:38:40.985 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: ...they're going
to have to rewind this...

00:38:40.985 --> 00:38:42.320 align:middle line:90%
>> Delgado: Right.

00:38:42.320 --> 00:38:43.121 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: ...and say, "Okay,
let me write that down again."

00:38:43.121 --> 00:38:44.289 align:middle line:90%
What does this show up as?

00:38:44.289 --> 00:38:45.657 align:middle line:84%
Do you have an -- this is
part of the EstroBlock?

00:38:45.657 --> 00:38:46.324 align:middle line:90%
>> Delgado: Yeah.

00:38:46.324 --> 00:38:47.425 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:38:47.425 --> 00:38:49.394 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: They either
have regular EstroBlock

00:38:49.394 --> 00:38:50.428 align:middle line:90%
which is not a soy-based.

00:38:50.428 --> 00:38:52.497 align:middle line:84%
Some of the delivery
systems you would...

00:38:52.497 --> 00:38:53.565 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:38:53.565 --> 00:38:54.532 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: ...use a
soy lecithin delivery.

00:38:54.532 --> 00:38:56.301 align:middle line:84%
We don't. We're smarter
than that.

00:38:56.301 --> 00:39:00.205 align:middle line:84%
We knew that people might have
sensitivities to soy, or --

00:39:00.205 --> 00:39:02.373 align:middle line:84%
or colors, or chemicals,
or excipeients,

00:39:02.373 --> 00:39:04.509 align:middle line:84%
and additives, or
magnesium sterate.

00:39:04.509 --> 00:39:05.176 align:middle line:90%
All...

00:39:05.176 --> 00:39:06.311 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yes.

00:39:06.311 --> 00:39:07.245 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: ...our
products are pure and clean.

00:39:07.245 --> 00:39:09.247 align:middle line:84%
So then I created
EstroBlock Pro.

00:39:09.247 --> 00:39:11.182 align:middle line:84%
And it's interesting, my staff
went, "Why are you doing this?

00:39:11.182 --> 00:39:14.986 align:middle line:84%
You're making a product that's
superior, three times stronger

00:39:14.986 --> 00:39:17.722 align:middle line:84%
than the EstroBlock you've
already released, and it's --

00:39:17.722 --> 00:39:19.490 align:middle line:84%
it's going to compete
with your own product."

00:39:19.490 --> 00:39:21.626 align:middle line:84%
And I said, "Well, some
people have cancer.

00:39:21.626 --> 00:39:23.528 align:middle line:90%
Some people have severe acne.

00:39:23.528 --> 00:39:24.395 align:middle line:90%
Some people are severely obese.

00:39:24.395 --> 00:39:26.464 align:middle line:90%
They need the triple strength.

00:39:26.464 --> 00:39:29.167 align:middle line:84%
They need the concentrations,
and they can get by with two

00:39:29.167 --> 00:39:31.336 align:middle line:84%
or three tablets instead of
having to take five or six

00:39:31.336 --> 00:39:32.637 align:middle line:90%
of the EstroBlock regular."

00:39:32.637 --> 00:39:35.640 align:middle line:84%
It was a slightly more cost,
maybe $10 more, but people...

00:39:35.640 --> 00:39:37.075 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:39:37.075 --> 00:39:38.142 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: It ended up
turning out that I was right.

00:39:38.142 --> 00:39:40.211 align:middle line:84%
Not that I'm right, and
you're wrong, but --

00:39:40.211 --> 00:39:41.246 align:middle line:84%
but people, the consumers
said, "Wow!

00:39:41.246 --> 00:39:44.582 align:middle line:84%
I can get this at --
at much less price,"

00:39:44.582 --> 00:39:47.252 align:middle line:84%
and there's literally EstroBlock
knock-offs now on the market.

00:39:47.252 --> 00:39:48.286 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:39:48.286 --> 00:39:48.987 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: They're
copying my name...

00:39:48.987 --> 00:39:50.021 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Right.

00:39:50.021 --> 00:39:51.356 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: ...that
I came out in 2003

00:39:51.356 --> 00:39:54.626 align:middle line:84%
and actually had created the
science in early 2001, and --

00:39:54.626 --> 00:39:56.127 align:middle line:90%
and released the prototypes.

00:39:56.127 --> 00:39:57.262 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: And this
goes for men, too.

00:39:57.262 --> 00:39:58.496 align:middle line:90%
This isn't just for women.

