Can you talk about that?

00:40:07.672 --> 00:40:09.240 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: Arnold
Schwarzenegger came to speak

00:40:09.240 --> 00:40:11.276 align:middle line:90%
at our event just two weeks ago.

00:40:11.276 --> 00:40:15.680 align:middle line:84%
His look-alike who in earlier
movies had some issues,

