>> Delgado: They want to
do breast removal surgery.

00:40:20.785 --> 00:40:22.220 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Oh, no.

00:40:22.220 --> 00:40:23.054 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: Because most
of the body builders --

00:40:23.054 --> 00:40:24.122 align:middle line:90%
they won't tell you this --

00:40:24.122 --> 00:40:26.157 align:middle line:84%
they take so much
synthetic testosterone

00:40:26.157 --> 00:40:28.559 align:middle line:84%
that it causes abnormal
increase in estrogens.

00:40:28.559 --> 00:40:29.694 align:middle line:90%
And ironically men,

00:40:29.694 --> 00:40:32.430 align:middle line:84%
who initially they see
these commercials on TV,

00:40:32.430 --> 00:40:35.566 align:middle line:84%
you know low T, go to your
doctor and get testosterone.

00:40:35.566 --> 00:40:37.168 align:middle line:84%
Little do they realize,
particularly

00:40:37.168 --> 00:40:39.570 align:middle line:84%
if they're a little overweight,
if they take testosterone cream

00:40:39.570 --> 00:40:41.506 align:middle line:84%
