or they don't know

00:40:41.506 --> 00:40:44.642 align:middle line:84%
about what I'm going to share
with you how the herbs interact,

00:40:44.642 --> 00:40:47.045 align:middle line:84%
then what happens is they
start developing breast tissue.

00:40:47.045 --> 00:40:48.579 align:middle line:84%
They get big muscles, but
they get breast tissue, too.

00:40:48.579 --> 00:40:51.049 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: Yeah, have to
wear a bro.

00:40:51.049 --> 00:40:53.451 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: And then they
start losing sexual function.

00:40:53.451 --> 00:40:54.585 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Yeah.

00:40:54.585 --> 00:40:55.653 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: And -- and a
whole host of problems.

00:40:55.653 --> 00:40:59.157 align:middle line:84%
So what I discovered
was change the diet;

00:40:59.157 --> 00:41:00.391 align:middle line:84%
they're eating way
too much meat.

00:41:00.391 --> 00:41:03.094 align:middle line:84%
And believe me, these big body
builders can get as massive,

00:41:03.094 --> 00:41:04.262 align:middle line:84%
trust me, eating a
plant-based diet.

00:41:04.262 --> 00:41:06.497 align:middle line:84%
Gorillas, look at
them, massively...

00:41:06.497 --> 00:41:08.099 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Exactly.

00:41:08.099 --> 00:41:10.134 align:middle line:84%
>> Delgado: ...the most powerful
animal -- animals on the planet.

00:41:10.134 --> 00:41:11.169 align:middle line:84%
They -- they absorb
large amounts of nitrogen

00:41:11.169 --> 00:41:14.539 align:middle line:90%
from nitrogenous-based plants.

00:41:14.539 --> 00:41:17.008 align:middle line:84%
I use a lot of nitric
oxide foods,

00:41:17.008 --> 00:41:18.309 align:middle line:90%
and we'll talk about that later.

00:41:18.309 --> 00:41:20.278 align:middle line:90%
Kale, Swiss chard, arugula.

00:41:20.278 --> 00:41:22.513 align:middle line:84%
It's just amazing what it
does for body building.

