the saliva, and so forth.

00:41:43.368 --> 00:41:44.135 align:middle line:90%
>> Delgado: That's right.

00:41:44.135 --> 00:41:45.236 align:middle line:90%
>> Regina: Determine --

00:41:45.236 --> 00:41:46.337 align:middle line:84%
but anyway the point is
you've created something

00:41:46.337 --> 00:41:47.605 align:middle line:90%
that does counter that.

